posts.subject: The Dems will use the internet giants to silence
posts.body:
Intensifying .....

If there ever was a time to bridge Zeronet to the clearnet - it's now. So all will spill into emails, and postings from a mischievous public.

Death by a thousand cuts. No way to stop it. Reeeeeeeee will be magnificent.


This effort should be named in the honor of a real bullshit deflator. 

"The John Belushi fix."

Make it craptacular. Post in Russian for the lultz.
